OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FEngland fans expressed frustration and
OL,8,Fdisappointment following their 0-0
OL,9,FWorld Cup draw with Ghana, but
OL,10,Finsisted football is "still coming
OL,11,Fhome".
OL,13,FThomas Tuchel's team struggled to
OL,14,Fbreak through Ghana's defence amid
OL,15,Fmore hydration break controversy.
OL,17,FSupporters who made the trip to the
OL,18,FBoston Stadium in Foxborough in
OL,19,FMassachusetts on Tuesday said they
OL,20,Fstill believed the Three Lions would
OL,21,Ftop the group.
OL,26,@rD@VOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
