PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FCharlie Gould added: "It's a great
OL,8,Fexperience to come to the stadium, but
OL,9,Fit's disappointing to draw with Ghana.
OL,10,FHopefully better to come against
OL,11,FPanama."
OL,13,FSome England fans said the chance for
OL,14,FHarry Kane near the end of the game
OL,15,Fcould have changed the mood among
OL,16,Fsupporters.
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
