OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FFreddie Kenison, 32, from Hatfield in
OL,8,FHertfordshire, said: "The Harry Kane
OL,9,Fchance could have changed everything `
OL,10,Fwe'd have all been buzzing if that had
OL,11,Fgone in.
OL,13,F"It wasn't the most inspiring
OL,14,Fperformance."
OL,16,FMuch of the England faithful's focus
OL,17,Fduring Tuesday's game was placed on
OL,18,Fbooing both the hydration breaks and
OL,19,FGhanaian midfielder Thomas Partey.
OL,26,@pD@VOUuD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
