OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FThe first half saw stoppage time for
OL,8,Fan injury and instead of that being
OL,9,Fused for the hydration break, it was
OL,10,Fheld in the 26th minute in line with
OL,11,Fother games.
OL,13,FEngland supporters were very vocal and
OL,14,Floudly booing the mid-half drinks
OL,15,Fbreaks.
OL,17,FCommenting on the hydration break, 32-
OL,18,Fyear-old England fan Sam Jeatar, from
OL,19,FLondon, told PA: "It's 20 degrees
OL,20,Fhere, it's 37 at home.
OL,26,@{D@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
