OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,F"We all know what that is ` it's a
OL,8,Fmoney grab.
OL,10,F"We shouldn't be too surprised that
OL,11,Fthey are looking for a bit more cash.
OL,13,F"Bit of a joke really ` we were
OL,14,Fbooing. Heavily."
OL,16,FFIFA told PA that hydration breaks are
OL,17,Fimplemented "involving all teams in
OL,18,Fevery match, so matches are played
OL,19,Funder the same conditions".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUvD@QO]yD@MOU{D@ZO]
