OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FTheir statement added: "We want to
OL,8,Fensure equal conditions for everyone,
OL,9,Fand that's why these breaks are
OL,10,Fimplemented in every match."
OL,12,FElsewhere, Djed Spence appeared to
OL,13,Fsnub a handshake with former Arsenal
OL,14,Fmidfielder Partey ahead of the clash
OL,15,Fin Boston.
OL,17,FHe was denied entry to Canada for
OL,18,FGhana's first World Cup game, having
OL,19,Fbeen charged with seven counts of rape
OL,20,Fand one count of sexual assault in
OL,21,FLondon between 2020 and 2022.
OL,26,@oD@XOUrD@\O]
