OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FPartey told officials in the host
OL,8,Fcountry that he had never been
OL,9,Farrested or charged with a crime. He
OL,10,Fdenies all charges and is set to stand
OL,11,Ftrial next summer.
OL,13,FBack in the UK, England fans flocked
OL,14,Fto watch parties in Wembley,
OL,15,FManchester, Nottingham and Newcastle
OL,16,Fahead of the match.
OL,18,FThe heat did not keep supporters away
OL,19,Fafter temperatures reached 34.6C in
OL,20,Fthe UK earlier in the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
