OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782267480
OL,3,CFrustration and disappointment for
OL,4,CEngland fans following 0-0 draw with
OL,5,CGhana
OL,7,FMany donned England shirts and some
OL,8,Fwere seen with handheld fans, while
OL,9,Fothers wore hats to stay cool.
OL,11,FEngland's final World Cup group game
OL,12,Ftakes place on Saturday at the MetLife
OL,13,Fstadium in New Jersey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
